## Theme: Cool Onyx with Mint accents

Primary: #16FFBB → 156 100% 54% (electric mint)
Accent: #29DDDA → 179 70% 51% (vivid cyan)
Background: #0D0F12 → 220 16% 6% (cool onyx — neutral dark with minimal cold undertone)

Surfaces use hue 220 with low saturation (8-16%) and increasing lightness (6% → 19%).
Neutral background lets mint/cyan accents pop without color bleeding.

## Typography
- Display/Headings: Space Grotesk (tech-security character)
- Body: Space Grotesk
- Mono (IDs, metrics, terminal): JetBrains Mono
- AI prose: IBM Plex Serif

## Severity Visual Language
- Critical: red ambient glow on card, red stripe, pulsing dot, ⚡ icon
- High: orange stripe, ⚠ icon
- Medium: yellow stripe, ● icon
- Low: blue stripe, ℹ icon
Each severity has `ambient`, `stripe`, and `icon` properties in getSeverityColor().

## Living Background
Noise texture overlay (0.025 opacity) + animated mesh gradient orbs (slow rotation) + vignette edge darkening.
